      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 63,
      "message": "yes we can use only synchronized marker and no we should do not do this 😊\nI would to secure restartAplication method. When someone, in the future or by accident, will change the order of method invocation, for example: startListening... then startApplication, I want to be sure that application will still work correctly. That is why I used ReentrantLock.",
